    <entry>
      <title>Spring Security下整合多种登录方式设计</title>
      <link href="/2026/04/06/Spring-Security%E4%B8%8BDao%E4%B8%8ESms%E5%85%B1%E5%AD%98%E7%9A%84AuthenticationProvider%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1/"/>
      <url>/2026/04/06/Spring-Security%E4%B8%8BDao%E4%B8%8ESms%E5%85%B1%E5%AD%98%E7%9A%84AuthenticationProvider%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>在Spring Security项目中，其提供的默认的DaoAuthenticationProvider（账号密码登录）往往不足以满足项目需求。</p><p>在比较复杂的项目中往往需要多种登录方式并存来进行验证和授权。</p><p>本文将以DaoAuthenticationProvider与SmsAuthenticationProvider共存的例子讲解Spring Security如何整合多种登录方式。</p></blockquote><h1 id="Spring-Security验证授权调用链"><a href="#Spring-Security验证授权调用链" class="headerlink" title="Spring Security验证授权调用链"></a>Spring Security验证授权调用链</h1><p>以DaoAuthenticationProvider为例，其验证授权调用链如下：</p><p><img src="https://s1.imagehub.cc/images/2026/04/06/b4102f334914881e37ad1b7940d4bf10.png" alt="Spring Security Call Chain"></p><p>不难发现若我们要实现短信验证码登录，需要实现<code>SmsAuthenticationToken</code>、<code>SmsAuthenticationProvider</code>、<code>SmsUserDetailsService</code>、<code>SmsUserDetails</code>。</p><p>由<code>SmsAuthenticationProvider</code>调用<code>authenticate(Authentication)</code>方法，并在此方法中调用<code>SmsUserDetailsService</code>的<code>loadUserByUsername(String)</code>方法，返回<code>SmsUserDetails</code>。</p><p>接下来我们由下而上实现整个链路。</p><h1 id="SmsAuthService"><a href="#SmsAuthService" class="headerlink" title="SmsAuthService"></a>SmsAuthService</h1><blockquote><p>这个类用于实现短信验证码状态管理以及验证码比对。</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">package</span> top.whaleghost.appointmentsystem.core.security;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> lombok.RequiredArgsConstructor;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> lombok.extern.slf4j.Slf4j;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Value;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.data.redis.core.StringRedisTemplate;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.stereotype.Component;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.util.Random;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.util.concurrent.TimeUnit;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Slf4j</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@RequiredArgsConstructor</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Component</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">SmsAuthService</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@Value(&quot;$&#123;app.main-body-name&#125;&quot;)</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> String mainBodyName;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">final</span> StringRedisTemplate verificationCodeRedisTemplate;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">sendVerificationCode</span><span class="params">(String phoneNumber)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">String</span> <span class="variable">verificationCode</span> <span class="operator">=</span> generateVerificationCode();</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// Todo: 调用短信服务</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">String</span> <span class="variable">key</span> <span class="operator">=</span> mainBodyName + <span class="string">&quot;:sms:code:&quot;</span> + phoneNumber;</span><br><span class="line">        verificationCodeRedisTemplate.opsForValue().set(</span><br><span class="line">                key, verificationCode, <span class="number">5</span>, TimeUnit.MINUTES</span><br><span class="line">        );</span><br><span class="line">        log.info(<span class="string">&quot;SmsAuthService: Code[&#123;&#125;] =&gt; phone[&#123;&#125;] has been sent.&quot;</span>, verificationCode, phoneNumber);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="type">boolean</span> <span class="title function_">verifyCode</span><span class="params">(String phoneNumber, String verificationCode)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">String</span> <span class="variable">key</span> <span class="operator">=</span> mainBodyName + <span class="string">&quot;:sms:code:&quot;</span> + phoneNumber;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">String</span> <span class="variable">cache</span> <span class="operator">=</span> verificationCodeRedisTemplate.opsForValue().get(key);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (verificationCode.equals(cache)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            verificationCodeRedisTemplate.delete(key);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> String <span class="title function_">generateVerificationCode</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> String.valueOf(<span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Random</span>().nextInt(<span class="number">899999</span>) + <span class="number">100000</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>装配<code>StringRedisTemplate</code>以实现短信验证码保存。</p><p><code>generateVerificationCode()</code>方法用于生成6位随机验证码。</p><p><code>sendVerificationCode(String phoneNumber)</code>方法用于调用云服务商的SMS服务并发送短信验证码，同时将发送的验证码载入Redis实现过期自动删除与存储。</p><p><code>verifyCode(String phoneNumber, String verificationCode)</code>方法用于比对验证码是否存在并且正确。</p><h1 id="SmsAuthenticationToken"><a href="#SmsAuthenticationToken" class="headerlink" title="SmsAuthenticationToken"></a>SmsAuthenticationToken</h1><blockquote><p>这个类用于实现通行验证Token，类比<code>UsernamePasswordAuthenticationToken</code>。</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">package</span> top.whaleghost.appointmentsystem.core.security;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> lombok.Getter;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.authentication.AbstractAuthenticationToken;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.core.GrantedAuthority;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.util.Collection;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Getter</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">SmsAuthenticationToken</span> <span class="keyword">extends</span> <span class="title class_">AbstractAuthenticationToken</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">final</span> Object principal;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> Object credentials;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="title function_">SmsAuthenticationToken</span><span class="params">(String phoneNumber, String verificationCode)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">super</span>((Collection&lt;? <span class="keyword">extends</span> <span class="title class_">GrantedAuthority</span>&gt;) <span class="literal">null</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">this</span>.principal = phoneNumber;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">this</span>.credentials = verificationCode;</span><br><span class="line">        setAuthenticated(<span class="literal">false</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="title function_">SmsAuthenticationToken</span><span class="params">(</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">            Object principal, Object credentials, Collection&lt;? extends GrantedAuthority&gt; authorities</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">    )</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">super</span>(authorities);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">this</span>.principal = principal;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">this</span>.credentials = credentials;</span><br><span class="line">        setAuthenticated(<span class="literal">true</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>构造方法<code>SmsAuthenticationToken(String phoneNumber, String verificationCode)</code>用于构造在登录时的验证Token，授权封装为空，交由后续处理，<code>principal</code>、<code>credentials</code>分别与与<code>phoneNumber</code>、<code>verificationCode</code>绑定。</p><p>由于本系统的登录鉴权链路采用jwt方案设计，本项目的构造方法<code>SmsAuthenticationToken(Object principal, Object credentials, Collection&lt;? extends GrantedAuthority&gt; authorities)</code>用于构造用户在已登录系统并获得jwt后供<code>JwtAuthenticationFilter</code>过滤使用的Token，读者可以根据项目实际设计方案自行调整此构造方法。</p><h1 id="SmsUserDetails"><a href="#SmsUserDetails" class="headerlink" title="SmsUserDetails"></a>SmsUserDetails</h1><blockquote><p>此类用于构造用户信息以供后续授权使用。</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">package</span> top.whaleghost.appointmentsystem.core.security;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> lombok.AllArgsConstructor;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> lombok.Getter;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> lombok.NonNull;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> lombok.Setter;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.core.GrantedAuthority;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.core.authority.SimpleGrantedAuthority;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.core.userdetails.UserDetails;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> top.whaleghost.appointmentsystem.core.pojo.entity.rbac.Permission;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> top.whaleghost.appointmentsystem.core.pojo.entity.rbac.Role;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.util.Collection;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.util.HashSet;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.util.List;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.util.Set;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Getter</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Setter</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@AllArgsConstructor</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">SmsUserDetails</span> <span class="keyword">implements</span> <span class="title class_">UserDetails</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">final</span> String phoneNumber;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">final</span> String verificationCode;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">final</span> Integer currentStatus;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">final</span> List&lt;Role&gt; roles;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> SmsUserDetails <span class="title function_">create</span><span class="params">(</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">            String phoneNumber, String verificationCode, Integer currentStatus, List&lt;Role&gt; roles</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">    )</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">SmsUserDetails</span>(phoneNumber, verificationCode, currentStatus, roles);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@Override</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@NonNull</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> Collection&lt;? <span class="keyword">extends</span> <span class="title class_">GrantedAuthority</span>&gt; getAuthorities() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        Set&lt;GrantedAuthority&gt; authorities = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">HashSet</span>&lt;&gt;();</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (Role role : roles) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">for</span> (Permission permission : role.getPermissions()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                authorities.add(<span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">SimpleGrantedAuthority</span>(permission.getPermissionName()));</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> authorities;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@Override</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> String <span class="title function_">getPassword</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> verificationCode;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@Override</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@NonNull</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> String <span class="title function_">getUsername</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> phoneNumber;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@Override</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="type">boolean</span> <span class="title function_">isEnabled</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> currentStatus == <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>读者需要注意，只有<code>phoneNumber</code>、<code>verificationCode</code>、<code>roles</code>字段必须实现，其他字段为可选项，根据项目设计方案自行调整。</p><p>由于本项目采用权限组方案，所以<code>Role</code>只负责整合<code>Permisson</code>，本身不作为权限进行使用，所以在<code>getAuthorities()</code>方法中并没有将<code>role</code>信息也载入至<code>authorities</code>。</p><h1 id="SmsUserDetailsService"><a href="#SmsUserDetailsService" class="headerlink" title="SmsUserDetailsService"></a>SmsUserDetailsService</h1><blockquote><p>这个类没有难点，它的职责有且只有将用户信息从数据库中带出。</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">package</span> top.whaleghost.appointmentsystem.core.security;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> lombok.RequiredArgsConstructor;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.jspecify.annotations.NonNull;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.core.userdetails.UserDetails;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.core.userdetails.UserDetailsService;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.core.userdetails.UsernameNotFoundException;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.stereotype.Service;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> top.whaleghost.appointmentsystem.core.pojo.entity.rbac.Employee;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> top.whaleghost.appointmentsystem.core.pojo.entity.transaction.Customer;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> top.whaleghost.appointmentsystem.core.repository.CustomerRepo;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> top.whaleghost.appointmentsystem.core.repository.EmployeeRepo;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.util.ArrayList;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@RequiredArgsConstructor</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Service</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">SmsUserDetailsService</span> <span class="keyword">implements</span> <span class="title class_">UserDetailsService</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">final</span> CustomerRepo customerRepo;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">final</span> EmployeeRepo employeeRepo;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@Override</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@NonNull</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> UserDetails <span class="title function_">loadUserByUsername</span><span class="params">(<span class="meta">@NonNull</span> String phoneNumber)</span> <span class="keyword">throws</span> UsernameNotFoundException &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">Employee</span> <span class="variable">employee</span> <span class="operator">=</span> employeeRepo.findEmployeeByPhoneNumber(phoneNumber).orElse(<span class="literal">null</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">Customer</span> <span class="variable">customer</span> <span class="operator">=</span> customerRepo.findCustomerByPhoneNumber(phoneNumber).orElse(<span class="literal">null</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (employee != <span class="literal">null</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> SmsUserDetails.create(</span><br><span class="line">                    employee.getPhoneNumber(), <span class="literal">null</span>, employee.getCurrentStatus(), employee.getRoles()</span><br><span class="line">            );</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (customer != <span class="literal">null</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> SmsUserDetails.create(</span><br><span class="line">                    customer.getPhoneNumber(), <span class="literal">null</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">ArrayList</span>&lt;&gt;()</span><br><span class="line">            );</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">throw</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">UsernameNotFoundException</span>(<span class="string">&quot;用户不存在&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>装配<code>CustomerRepo</code>、<code>EmployeeRepo</code>以查询用户信息。</p><p>由于作者的项目SMS登录服务同时对后台和前台暴露，<code>loadUserByUsername(@NonNull String phoneNumber)</code>方法对数据库进行了两次查询，读者可以根据自己的项目实际情况调整，大致思路就是去数据库中查询用户信息并返回。</p><h1 id="SmsAuthenticationProvider"><a href="#SmsAuthenticationProvider" class="headerlink" title="SmsAuthenticationProvider"></a>SmsAuthenticationProvider</h1><blockquote><p>这个类用来截获SmsAuthenticationToken并进行验证授权。</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">package</span> top.whaleghost.appointmentsystem.core.security;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> lombok.RequiredArgsConstructor;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.jspecify.annotations.NonNull;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.authentication.AuthenticationProvider;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.authentication.BadCredentialsException;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.core.Authentication;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.core.AuthenticationException;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.core.userdetails.UserDetails;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.stereotype.Component;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@RequiredArgsConstructor</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Component</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">SmsAuthenticationProvider</span> <span class="keyword">implements</span> <span class="title class_">AuthenticationProvider</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">final</span> SmsUserDetailsService smsUserDetailsService;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">final</span> SmsAuthService smsAuthService;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@Override</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> Authentication <span class="title function_">authenticate</span><span class="params">(<span class="meta">@NonNull</span> Authentication authentication)</span> <span class="keyword">throws</span> AuthenticationException &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">SmsAuthenticationToken</span> <span class="variable">smsAuth</span> <span class="operator">=</span> (SmsAuthenticationToken) authentication;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">String</span> <span class="variable">phoneNumber</span> <span class="operator">=</span> (String) smsAuth.getPrincipal();</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">String</span> <span class="variable">verificationCode</span> <span class="operator">=</span> (String) smsAuth.getCredentials();</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (!smsAuthService.verifyCode(phoneNumber, verificationCode)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">throw</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">BadCredentialsException</span>(<span class="string">&quot;验证码错误或已过期&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">UserDetails</span> <span class="variable">smsCustomerDetails</span> <span class="operator">=</span> smsUserDetailsService.loadUserByUsername(phoneNumber);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">SmsAuthenticationToken</span> <span class="variable">result</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">SmsAuthenticationToken</span>(</span><br><span class="line">                smsCustomerDetails,</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="literal">null</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                smsCustomerDetails.getAuthorities()</span><br><span class="line">        );</span><br><span class="line">        result.setDetails(smsAuth.getDetails());</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> result;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@Override</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="type">boolean</span> <span class="title function_">supports</span><span class="params">(<span class="meta">@NonNull</span> Class&lt;?&gt; authentication)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> SmsAuthenticationToken.class.isAssignableFrom(authentication);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>装配<code>SmsUserDetailsService</code>以进行数据库用户信息拉取，装配<code>SmsAuthService</code>以进行短信验证码核验。</p><p><code>supports(@NonNull Class&lt;?&gt; authentication)</code>方法负责告诉Spring Security在接收到不同类型的<code>AuthenticationToken</code>时该使用哪个<code>AuthenticationTokenProvider</code>。我的<code>SmsAuthenticationProvider</code>只期望接取<code>SmsAuthenticationToken</code>，所以使用此方法将两者进行绑定。</p><h1 id="AuthenticationManager"><a href="#AuthenticationManager" class="headerlink" title="AuthenticationManager"></a>AuthenticationManager</h1><blockquote><p>这个Spring Security配置类用于注入你的<code>SmsAuthenticationProvider</code>。</p><p>⚠️值得注意的时，在你决定注入自定义的<code>SmsAuthenticationProvider</code>后，若不进行人为干预，Spring Security默认提供的<code>DaoAuthenticationProvider</code>将会被禁用，若需要保留，则需要手动进行注入。</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">package</span> top.whaleghost.appointmentsystem.web.config;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Qualifier;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.context.annotation.Bean;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.context.annotation.Configuration;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.authentication.AuthenticationManager;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.authentication.AuthenticationProvider;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.authentication.ProviderManager;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.authentication.dao.DaoAuthenticationProvider;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.config.annotation.method.configuration.EnableMethodSecurity;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.config.annotation.web.builders.HttpSecurity;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.config.annotation.web.configuration.EnableWebSecurity;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.config.annotation.web.configurers.AbstractHttpConfigurer;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.config.http.SessionCreationPolicy;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.core.userdetails.UserDetailsService;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.crypto.bcrypt.BCryptPasswordEncoder;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.web.SecurityFilterChain;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.web.authentication.UsernamePasswordAuthenticationFilter;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.web.authentication.logout.LogoutHandler;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.security.web.authentication.logout.SecurityContextLogoutHandler;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> org.springframework.web.cors.CorsConfiguration;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> top.whaleghost.appointmentsystem.util.NetworkEnvUtil;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> top.whaleghost.appointmentsystem.web.filter.JwtAuthenticationFilter;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.util.ArrayList;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.util.Arrays;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.util.List;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Configuration</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@EnableWebSecurity</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@EnableMethodSecurity</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">SecurityConfig</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// existing code...</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@Bean</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> AuthenticationProvider <span class="title function_">daoAuthenticationProvider</span><span class="params">(</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">            <span class="meta">@Qualifier(&quot;normalUserDetailsService&quot;)</span> UserDetailsService normalUserDetailsService</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">    )</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">DaoAuthenticationProvider</span> <span class="variable">provider</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">DaoAuthenticationProvider</span>(normalUserDetailsService);</span><br><span class="line">        provider.setPasswordEncoder(<span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">BCryptPasswordEncoder</span>());</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> provider;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@Bean</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> AuthenticationManager <span class="title function_">authenticationManager</span><span class="params">(</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">            <span class="meta">@Qualifier(&quot;smsAuthenticationProvider&quot;)</span> AuthenticationProvider smsAuthenticationProvider,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">            <span class="meta">@Qualifier(&quot;daoAuthenticationProvider&quot;)</span> AuthenticationProvider daoAuthenticationProvider</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">    )</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">ProviderManager</span>(</span><br><span class="line">                Arrays.asList(smsAuthenticationProvider, daoAuthenticationProvider)</span><br><span class="line">        );</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// existing code...</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>由于Spring Security中如何使用<code>DaoAuthenticationProvider</code>配合数据库中的账号密码进行登录教程诸多，本文章便不再进行<code>normalUserDetailsService</code>的讲解。</p><h1 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h1><p>Spring Security中由<code>AuthenticationManager</code>对所有的<code>AuthenticationProvider</code>进行管理，接收到不同的<code>AuthenticationToken</code>时会依次调用每个<code>AuthenticationProvider</code>的<code>supports(@NonNull Class&lt;?&gt; authentication)</code>方法进行匹配，匹配成功后执行这个<code>AuthenticationProvider</code>的<code>authenticate(@NonNull Authentication authentication)</code>方法并传导至与数据库交互的<code>UserDetailsService</code>的<code>loadUserByUsername(@Nonnull String username)</code>方法，拉取数据库结果成功后再由<code>AuthenticationProvider</code>决定是否放行，最后返回包含所有信息的<code>Authentication</code>（注意抹除敏感字段如密码等）。</p>]]></content>
      
      
